    under rising-tone _(2)tsoi_ (zoi2) rather than departing-tone _tsoi(3)_ (zoi3)^,
    noting I have not seen solid evidence to back up my decision.
    I am happy to be proven wrong, and for Williams to be vindicated.
  ====
